6. Problem of the Day : https://leetcode.com/problems/delete-nodes-and-return-forest/solutions/5491937/100-easy-solution-post-order-traversal-easy-to-apply/
These challenges pushed me to apply my understanding of algorithms and data structures effectively. Each problem taught me valuable lessons in optimization and problem-solving strategies.

